mention.text: OKLAHOMA CITY -- It could not happen .
Seconds after an Isaiah Taylor floater
senior forward Paul Jesperson for a ceremonial half-court heave
We kind of felt like this
A group of five Longhorn seniors
the postseason demons that had haunted the group for so long
Paul Jesperson for a ceremonial half-court heave
the left side of the floor
the source of tears -- both of sadness and joy
a Longhorn team that had seemingly put everything together when it mattered most
a moment that will likely haunt the Longhorns for every march to come
that way to lose on anybody
the punctuation of a career arc that seemingly never could stay on an upward trajectory
a great moment for us all
